#: ../../../event-logging.rst:4
msgid "Event Logging"
msgstr "事件日誌紀錄"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:6
msgid "Vyper can log events to be caught and displayed by user interfaces."
msgstr "Vyper 可以記錄事件，以便由使用者介面捕獲和顯示。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:9
msgid "Example of Logging"
msgstr "日誌紀錄範例"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:11
msgid ""
"This example is taken from the `sample ERC20 contract <https://github.com/"
"vyperlang/vyper/blob/master/examples/tokens/ERC20.vy>`_ and shows the basic "
"flow of event logging:"
msgstr ""
"此範例取自 `ERC20 合約範例 <https://github.com/vyperlang/vyper/blob/master/"
"examples/tokens/ERC20.vy>`_，展示了事件日誌紀錄的基本流程："

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:13
msgid ""
"# Events of the token.\n"
"event Transfer:\n"
"    sender: indexed(address)\n"
"    receiver: indexed(address)\n"
"    value: uint256\n"
"\n"
"event Approval:\n"
"    owner: indexed(address)\n"
"    spender: indexed(address)\n"
"    value: uint256\n"
"\n"
"# Transfer some tokens from message sender to another address\n"
"@external\n"
"def transfer(_to : address, _value : uint256) -> bool:\n"
"\n"
"   ... Logic here to do the real work ...\n"
"\n"
"   # All done, log the event for listeners\n"
"   log Transfer(sender=msg.sender, receiver=_to, value=_value)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:35
msgid "Let's look at what this is doing."
msgstr "讓我們看看這段程式碼在做什麼。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:37
msgid ""
"We declare two event types to log. The two events are similar in that they "
"contain two indexed address fields. Indexed fields do not make up part of "
"the event data itself, but can be searched by clients that want to catch the "
"event. Also, each event contains one single data field, in each case called "
"``value``. Events can contain several arguments with any names desired."
msgstr ""
"我們宣告了兩個要記錄的事件型別。這兩個事件相似之處在於都包含兩個已索引的地址"
"欄位。已索引欄位不構成事件資料本身的一部分，但可以由想要捕獲事件的客戶端進行"
"搜尋。此外，每個事件都包含一個資料欄位，在每個案例中稱為 ``value``。事件可以"
"包含多個任意名稱的引數。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:38
msgid ""
"In the ``transfer`` function, after we do whatever work is necessary, we log "
"the event. We pass three arguments, corresponding with the three arguments "
"of the Transfer event declaration."
msgstr ""
"在 ``transfer`` 函數中，在我們執行完必要的工作後，我們記錄事件。我們傳遞三個"
"引數，對應 Transfer 事件宣告的三個引數。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:40
msgid ""
"Clients listening to the events will declare and handle the events they are "
"interested in using a `library such as web3.js <https://solidity.readthedocs."
"io/en/latest/contracts.html#events>`_:"
msgstr ""
"監聽事件的客戶端將使用 `如 web3.js 的函式庫 <https://solidity.readthedocs.io/"
"en/latest/contracts.html#events>`_ 來宣告和處理他們感興趣的事件："

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:42
msgid ""
"var abi = /* abi as generated by the compiler */;\n"
"var MyToken = web3.eth.contract(abi);\n"
"var myToken = MyToken.at(\"0x1234...ab67\" /* address */);\n"
"\n"
"// watch for changes in the callback\n"
"var event = myToken.Transfer(function(error, result) {\n"
"    if (!error) {\n"
"        var args = result.returnValues;\n"
"        console.log('value transferred = ', args._amount);\n"
"    }\n"
"});"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:56
msgid ""
"In this example, the listening client declares the event to listen for. Any "
"time the contract sends this log event, the callback will be invoked."
msgstr ""
"在此範例中，監聽客戶端宣告了要監聽的事件。每當合約發送此日誌事件時，回呼就會"
"被呼叫。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:59
msgid "Declaring Events"
msgstr "宣告事件"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:61
msgid "Let's look at an event declaration in more detail."
msgstr "讓我們更詳細地看看事件宣告。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:63
msgid ""
"event Transfer:\n"
"    sender: indexed(address)\n"
"    receiver: indexed(address)\n"
"    value: uint256"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:70
msgid ""
"The EVM currently has five opcodes for emitting event logs: ``LOG0``, "
"``LOG1``, ``LOG2``, ``LOG3``, and ``LOG4``. These opcodes can be used to "
"create log records, where each log record consists of both **topics** and "
"**data**. Topics are 32-byte ''words'' that are used to describe what is "
"happening in an event. While topics are searchable, data is not. Event data "
"is however not limited, which means that you can include large or "
"complicated data like arrays or strings. Different opcodes (``LOG0`` through "
"``LOG4``) allow for different numbers of topics. For instance, ``LOG1`` "
"includes one topic, ``LOG2`` includes two topics, and so on. Event "
"declarations look similar to struct declarations, containing one or more "
"arguments that are passed to the event. Typical events will contain two "
"kinds of arguments:"
msgstr ""
"EVM 目前有五個用於發送事件日誌的 opcode：``LOG0``、``LOG1``、``LOG2``、"
"``LOG3`` 和 ``LOG4``。這些 opcode 可用於建立日誌記錄，其中每個日誌記錄由**主"
"題（topics）**和**資料（data）**組成。主題是 32 位元組的「字組」，用於描述事"
"件中發生的情況。雖然主題是可搜尋的，但資料不是。然而事件資料不受限制，這意味"
"著您可以包含大型或複雜的資料，如陣列或字串。不同的 opcode（``LOG0`` 到 "
"``LOG4``）允許不同數量的主題。例如，``LOG1`` 包含一個主題，``LOG2`` 包含兩個"
"主題，依此類推。事件宣告看起來類似於結構宣告，包含一個或多個傳遞給事件的引"
"數。典型的事件將包含兩種引數："

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:79
msgid ""
"**Indexed** arguments (topics), which can be searched for by listeners. Each "
"indexed argument is identified by the ``indexed`` keyword.  Here, each "
"indexed argument is an address. You can have up to four indexed arguments "
"(``LOG4``), but indexed arguments are not passed directly to listeners, "
"although some of this information (such as the sender) may be available in "
"the listener's `results` object."
msgstr ""
"**已索引**引數（主題），可以被監聽器搜尋。每個已索引引數由 ``indexed`` 關鍵字"
"標識。在此處，每個已索引引數都是一個地址。您最多可以有四個已索引引數"
"（``LOG4``），但已索引引數不會直接傳遞給監聽器，儘管其中一些資訊（如發送者）"
"可能在監聽器的 `results` 物件中可用。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Value** arguments (data), which are passed through to listeners. You can "
"have any number of value arguments and they can have arbitrary names."
msgstr ""
"**值**引數（資料），會直接傳遞給監聽器。您可以有任意數量的值引數，且它們可以"
"具有任意名稱。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:82
msgid ""
"Note that the first topic of a log record consists of the signature of the "
"name of the event that occurred, including the types of its parameters. It "
"is also possible to create an event with no arguments. In this case, use the "
"``pass`` statement:"
msgstr ""
"請注意，日誌記錄的第一個主題由已發生事件名稱的簽名組成，包括其參數的型別。也"
"可以建立沒有引數的事件。在這種情況下，請使用 ``pass`` 陳述式："

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:85
msgid "event Foo: pass"
msgstr "event Foo: pass"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:90
msgid "Logging Events"
msgstr "日誌紀錄事件"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:92
msgid ""
"Once an event is declared, you can log (send) events. You can send events as "
"many times as you want to. Please note that events are stored in transaction "
"logs rather than contract state storage, making them significantly cheaper "
"than storage operations. However, the drawback is that events are not "
"available to contracts, only to clients."
msgstr ""
"一旦事件被宣告，您就可以記錄（發送）事件。您可以根據需要多次發送事件。請注"
"意，事件儲存在交易日誌中而非合約狀態儲存中，這使其比儲存操作便宜得多。然而，"
"缺點是事件對合約不可用，僅對客戶端可用。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:94
msgid "Logging events is done using the ``log`` statement:"
msgstr "記錄事件是使用 ``log`` 陳述式完成的："

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:96
msgid "log Transfer(sender=msg.sender, receiver=_to, value=_value)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:100
msgid ""
"The types of arguments given must match those used when declaring the event. "
"When using keyword arguments (as shown above), the order does not matter."
msgstr ""
"給定的引數型別必須與宣告事件時使用的型別相符。使用關鍵字引數時（如上所示），"
"順序不重要。"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:103
msgid "Listening for Events"
msgstr "監聽事件"

#: ../../../event-logging.rst:105
msgid ""
"In the example listener above, the ``result`` arg actually passes a `large "
"amount of information <https://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/v1.2.6/web3-eth-"
"contract.html#contract-events-return>`_. Here we're most interested in "
"``result.returnValues``. This is an object with properties that match the "
"properties declared in the event. Note that this object does not contain the "
"indexed properties, which can only be searched in the original ``myToken."
"Transfer`` that created the callback."
msgstr ""
"在上面的監聽器範例中，``result`` 引數實際上傳遞了`大量資訊 <https://web3js."
"readthedocs.io/en/v1.2.6/web3-eth-contract.html#contract-events-return>`_。這"
"裡我們最感興趣的是 ``result.returnValues``。這是一個屬性與事件中宣告的屬性相"
"符的物件。請注意，此物件不包含已索引的屬性，這些屬性只能在建立回呼的原始 "
"``myToken.Transfer`` 中進行搜尋。"
